Text: FW hiddie ho CRYSTALBill NonPrivilegedpst Original Message From crystal hyde mailto Sent Tuesday August PM To Eriksson Fredrik Subject hiddie ho Hey everyone I know this is late notice and all especially since last week was my last day but anyhow please stop by VQ after work tomorrow evening for a few drinks Since Im unemployed now Ill be there a bit early to reserve a table of course So I hope to see everyone there Take it easy CRystal Do You Yahoo Make international calls for as low as minute with Yahoo Messenger
